snippet.title: My thoughts on what's going on with Amber Heard and Johnny Depp.
snippet.description:
So I was listening to the story of what's going on with Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. I don't normally get into all the celebrity drama stuff but it's come up everywhere in my feed lately I thought I'd go ahead and give it a listen, see what's all the buzz, and I was a little surprised. 

You know what though? I'm happy Johnny Depp recorded it though. He needs evidence like this. It has become so easy for a women just to accuse a man of something and the man in seen as a scumbag for something that he might not have done. 

Stuff like that is what I do not agree with.
I feel that, YES, she should be fired from the movie Aquaman and made to pay Johnny back for what she did.



Girl hits herself in head with Hammer!
